nless local verification proves it necessary.\",\n  \"risks\": [\n    \"If the old osgi_R4_core dependency remains on the test classpath alongside the newer OSGi API, duplicate org.osgi.framework classes may make classpath order relevant.\",\n    \"The JAXB API dependency is API-only; tests that create a real JAXBContext may need to avoid requiring an implementation unless local Gradle verification shows one is already available transitively.\"\n  ]\n}", "textSignature": "{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0ab0d761158d4606016a42dd79abf081978baa2ee88b99d492\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}], "api": "openai-responses", "provider": "OCA", "model": "oca/gpt-5.5", "usage": {"input": 2579, "output": 1245, "cacheRead": 26112, "cacheWrite": 0, "totalTokens": 29936, "cost": {"input": 0, "output": 0, "cacheRead": 0, "cacheWrite": 0, "total": 0}}, "stopReason": "stop", "timestamp": 1782766956099, "responseId": "resp_0ab0d761158d4606016a42dd6cfe8c81979295f1e45b5a9b53"}, "toolResults": []}
